<td valign=center>
<h1> Spherical Easel </h1>
<p style="text-indent:0pt"> 
<h3> A spherical drawing program </h3>
</td>
</tr></table>
</center>

<p> <b>Spherical Easel</b> is a program for creating interactive
diagrams in spherical geometry.  It may be viewed as a companion to 
<a href="http://www.keypress.com/sketchpad/"> The Geometer's
Sketchpad</a> and <a href="http://cs.unm.edu/~joel/NonEuclid/NonEuclid.html">
Non-Euclid</a>, programs for studying Euclidean and hyperbolic geometry,
respectively.  

